txt.en: The sounds of the Enemy echo off the nearby cave walls
You should be careful around these bends in the caverns

<u>Skoironk Caverns</u>\n\qWith the Rangers of Ithilien establishing a foothold in the Slag-hills, the Enemy have retaliated. The Rangers seek to push subterranian forces from the caverns of Skoironk, back into the depths and far from the Host of the West.\q
More foes occupy the passageways up ahead

<u>The Towers of Teeth</u>\n\qWith the Rangers of Ithilien establishing a foothold in the Slag-hills, the Enemy have retaliated. The Rangers seek to disrupt the forces within the Towers of the Teeth watching over the plain of Dagorlad for the Host of the West.\q
The tower of Carchost is still occupied by the Enemy
The tower's foundation is in ruins and certainly unsafe
The foundation of Narchost is overrun with the Enemy
